In order to resolve the clipping issue and ensure the Data Report view behaves consistently with the Insights view (scrolling the entire page rather than a constrained inner area), I have refactored `components/FormAnalytics.tsx`.

### **Updates:**

1.  **Layout Strategy:**
    *   Switched from a fixed-height, flex-box layout to a natural flow layout (`min-h-full` instead of `h-full`). This matches the "Insights" tab behavior.
    *   Removed `overflow-hidden` from the main container, allowing the page to handle vertical scrolling.

2.  **Horizontal Scrolling:**
    *   Wrapped the data table in a container with `overflow-x-auto`. This adds a horizontal scrollbar at the bottom of the table when content is too wide, fulfilling the request for a "slide bar".

3.  **Sticky Header Adjustments:**
    *   To prevent "clipping" (穿模) and z-index conflicts during page scrolling, I removed the `sticky` positioning from the **table header** (`thead`). The **page header** (with the title and buttons) remains sticky (`top-0`), ensuring context is preserved while allowing the data to flow naturally underneath.
    *   Adjusted z-indices to ensure the sticky page header stays on top of table content.

These changes eliminate the clipping artifacts caused by nested scrolling contexts and provide a spacious, scrollable view for large datasets.

# Updated files:

## components/FormAnalytics.tsx

Refactor Data Report layout to use page-level vertical scrolling and container-level horizontal scrolling, fixing clipping issues.

```tsx
import React, { useState } from 'react';
import { FormTemplate, FormSubmission } from '../types';
import { 
  ArrowLeft, 
  Download, 
  BarChart, 
  Users, 
  Calendar,
  Share2,
  PieChart as PieIcon,
  TrendingUp,
  Table,
  FileSpreadsheet,
  Search,
  Eye,
  X,
  CreditCard,
  UserSquare,
  PenTool,
  Clock,
  FileText
} from 'lucide-react';
import { BarChart as ReChart, Bar, XAxis, YAxis, Tooltip, ResponsiveContainer, PieChart, Pie, Cell, Legend, AreaChart, Area, CartesianGrid } from 'recharts';

interface FormAnalyticsProps {
  form: FormTemplate;
  submissions: FormSubmission[];
  onBack: () => void;
  onShare: () => void;
}

const COLORS = ['#6366f1', '#10b981', '#f59e0b', '#ef4444', '#8b5cf6', '#ec4899'];

const FormAnalytics: React.FC<FormAnalyticsProps> = ({ form, submissions, onBack, onShare }) => {
  const [activeTab, setActiveTab] = useState<'REPORT' | 'INSIGHTS'>('REPORT');
  const [searchTerm, setSearchTerm] = useState('');
  const [selectedSubmission, setSelectedSubmission] = useState<FormSubmission | null>(null);

  // --- Derived Data for Insights ---

  // 1. Daily Submission Stats
  const dailyStats = React.useMemo(() => {
    const counts: Record<string, number> = {};
    // Generate last 7 days keys
    for(let i=6; i>=0; i--) {
        const d = new Date();
        d.setDate(d.getDate() - i);
        const key = d.toLocaleDateString('zh-CN', { month: '2-digit', day: '2-digit' });
        counts[key] = 0;
    }

    submissions.forEach(s => {
      const date = new Date(s.submittedAt).toLocaleDateString('zh-CN', { month: '2-digit', day: '2-digit' });
      if (counts[date] !== undefined) {
          counts[date]++;
      }
    });
    return Object.keys(counts).map(date => ({ name: date, count: counts[date] }));
  }, [submissions]);

  // 2. Analyze Select Fields
  const selectFieldStats = React.useMemo(() => {
    return form.fields
      .filter(f => f.type === 'SELECT')
      .map(field => {
        const counts: Record<string, number> = {};
        submissions.forEach(s => {
          const val = s.data[field.id] || '未填';
          counts[val] = (counts[val] || 0) + 1;
        });
        const data = Object.keys(counts).map(k => ({ name: k, value: counts[k] }));
        return { fieldName: field.label, data };
      });
  }, [form, submissions]);

  // --- Derived Data for Report ---
  const filteredSubmissions = React.useMemo(() => {
    return submissions.filter(s => {
       const searchLower = searchTerm.toLowerCase();
       // Search across all field values
       return Object.values(s.data).some(val => 
         String(val).toLowerCase().includes(searchLower)
       );
    }).sort((a, b) => new Date(b.submittedAt).getTime() - new Date(a.submittedAt).getTime());
  }, [submissions, searchTerm]);

  const handleExport = () => {
    const headers = ['提交时间', ...form.fields.map(f => f.label)].join(',');
    const rows = filteredSubmissions.map(s => {
        const date = new Date(s.submittedAt).toLocaleString('zh-CN');
        const values = form.fields.map(f => {
            const val = s.data[f.id];
            if (typeof val === 'object') return JSON.stringify(val).replace(/"/g, '""');
            return `"${String(val || '').replace(/"/g, '""')}"`;
        });
        return [date, ...values].join(',');
    });
    const csvContent = "\ufeff" + [headers, ...rows].join('\n');
    const blob = new Blob([csvContent], { type: 'text/csv;charset=utf-8;' });
    const url = URL.createObjectURL(blob);
    const link = document.createElement('a');
    link.href = url;
    link.download = `${form.title}_数据报表.csv`;
    document.body.appendChild(link);
    link.click();
    document.body.removeChild(link);
  };

  return (
    <div className="space-y-6 animate-fade-in min-h-full flex flex-col bg-gray-50/50">

      {/* Header - Sticky relative to page scroll */}
      <div className="bg-white px-6 py-4 shadow-sm border-b border-gray-200 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between gap-4 sticky top-0 z-30">
         <div className="flex items-center gap-4">
            <button onClick={onBack} className="text-gray-500 hover:bg-gray-100 p-2 rounded-lg transition-colors">
               <ArrowLeft size={20} />
            </button>
            <div>
               <h1 className="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 flex items-center gap-2">
                 {form.title}
               </h1>
               <div className="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-500 mt-0.5">
                  <span className={`w-2 h-2 rounded-full ${form.status === 'ACTIVE' ? 'bg-green-500' : 'bg-gray-300'}`}></span>
                  {form.status === 'ACTIVE' ? '正在收集中' : '未发布/已结束'}
                  <span className="mx-1">|</span>
                  共 {submissions.length} 条数据
               </div>
            </div>
         </div>

         {/* Tab Switcher */}
         <div className="flex bg-gray-100 p-1 rounded-lg self-start md:self-center">
            <button 
              onClick={() => setActiveTab('REPORT')}
              className={`px-4 py-1.5 rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-all flex items-center gap-2 ${activeTab === 'REPORT' ? 'bg-white text-indigo-600 shadow-sm' : 'text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700'}`}
            >
               <Table size={16} /> 数据报表
            </button>
            <button 
              onClick={() => setActiveTab('INSIGHTS')}
              className={`px-4 py-1.5 rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-all flex items-center gap-2 ${activeTab === 'INSIGHTS' ? 'bg-white text-indigo-600 shadow-sm' : 'text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700'}`}
            >
               <BarChart size={16} /> 数据明细
            </button>
         </div>

         <div className="flex gap-2">
            <button 
              onClick={onShare}
              className="bg-white border border-gray-200 text-gray-700 px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium hover:bg-gray-50 flex items-center gap-2 transition-colors"
            >
              <Share2 size={16} /> 分享
            </button>
            {activeTab === 'REPORT' && (
                <button 
                onClick={handleExport}
                className="bg-indigo-600 text-white px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium hover:bg-indigo-700 flex items-center gap-2 shadow-sm transition-colors"
                >
                <Download size={16} /> 导出
                </button>
            )}
         </div>
      </div>

      <div className="px-6 pb-6">

        {/* VIEW 1: REPORT (List of Data) */}
        {activeTab === 'REPORT' && (
           <div className="space-y-4 w-full">
              {/* Toolbar */}
              <div className="flex justify-between items-center bg-white p-2 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm shrink-0">
                 <div className="relative flex-1 max-w-md">
                    <Search size={16} className="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-gray-400" />
                    <input 
                      type="text" 
                      value={searchTerm}
                      onChange={(e) => setSearchTerm(e.target.value)}
                      placeholder="搜索填写内容..."
                      className="w-full pl-9 pr-4 py-2 border-none outline-none bg-transparent text-sm focus:ring-0"
                    />
                 </div>
                 <div className="px-4 text-xs text-gray-400 border-l border-gray-100">
                    显示 {filteredSubmissions.length} 条结果
                 </div>
              </div>

              {/* Data Table Container - Natural Flow with Horizontal Scroll */}
              <div className="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden relative">
                 <div className="overflow-x-auto custom-scrollbar pb-2">
                    <table className="w-full text-left text-sm whitespace-nowrap border-collapse">
                       <thead className="bg-gray-50 text-gray-600 font-bold border-b border-gray-200">
                          <tr>
                             <th className="p-4 w-16 text-center bg-gray-50 border-b border-gray-200">#</th>
                             <th className="p-4 min-w-[160px] bg-gray-50 border-b border-gray-200">提交时间</th>
                             {form.fields.map(f => (
                                <th key={f.id} className="p-4 min-w-[150px] bg-gray-50 border-b border-gray-200">{f.label}</th>
                             ))}
                             {/* Operation Column - Sticky Right */}
                             <th className="p-4 text-right sticky right-0 bg-gray-50 border-b border-gray-200 shadow-[-10px_0_10px_-5px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] z-10">操作</th>
                          </tr>
                       </thead>
                       <tbody className="divide-y divide-gray-100">
                          {filteredSubmissions.map((s, idx) => (
                             <tr key={s.id} className="hover:bg-indigo-50 transition-colors group">
                                <td className="p-4 text-center text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs">{submissions.length - idx}</td>
                                <td className="p-4 text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs">
                                   {new Date(s.submittedAt).toLocaleString('zh-CN')}
                                </td>
                                {form.fields.map(f => {
                                   const val = s.data[f.id];
                                   return (
                                      <td key={f.id} className="p-4 text-gray-800">
                                         {f.type === 'SIGNATURE' && val ? (
                                            <span className="text-xs text-green-600 bg-green-50 px-2 py-1 rounded border border-green-100 flex items-center w-fit gap-1"><PenTool size={10} /> 已签名</span>
                                         ) : (typeof val === 'object' ? (
                                            <span className="text-xs text-gray-400 italic">复杂数据</span>
                                         ) : (
                                            <div className="max-w-[300px] truncate" title={String(val)}>{String(val || '-')}</div>
                                         ))}
                                      </td>
                                   );
                                })}
                                {/* Operation Column Body - Sticky Right */}
                                <td className="p-4 text-right sticky right-0 bg-white group-hover:bg-indigo-50 shadow-[-10px_0_10px_-5px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] z-10 border-l border-transparent group-hover:border-indigo-100">
                                   <button 
                                     onClick={() => setSelectedSubmission(s)}
                                     className="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800 p-1.5 hover:bg-indigo-100 rounded-lg transition-colors text-xs font-bold flex items-center gap-1 ml-auto"
                                   >
                                      <Eye size={14} /> 查看
                                   </button>
                                </td>
                             </tr>
                          ))}
                          {filteredSubmissions.length === 0 && (
                             <tr>
                                <td colSpan={form.fields.length + 3} className="py-20 text-center text-gray-400">
                                   <FileSpreadsheet size={48} className="mx-auto mb-4 opacity-20" />
                                   <p>暂无数据</p>
                                </td>
                             </tr>
                          )}
                       </tbody>
                    </table>
                 </div>
              </div>
           </div>
        )}

        {/* VIEW 2: INSIGHTS (Stats & Charts) */}
        {activeTab === 'INSIGHTS' && (
           <div className="space-y-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto pb-20">

              {/* Stats Cards */}
              <div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
                 <div className="bg-white p-5 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
                    <div className="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
                       <p className="text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase">总回收量</p>
                       <div className="p-2 bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600 rounded-lg"><FileText size={16} /></div>
                    </div>
                    <h3 className="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-800">{submissions.length}</h3>
                 </div>

                 <div className="bg-white p-5 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
                    <div className="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
                       <p className="text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase">今日新增</p>
                       <div className="p-2 bg-green-50 text-green-600 rounded-lg"><Calendar size={16} /></div>
                    </div>
                    <h3 className="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-800">
                       {submissions.filter(s => new Date(s.submittedAt).toDateString() === new Date().toDateString()).length}
                    </h3>
                 </div>

                 <div className="bg-white p-5 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
                    <div className="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
                       <p className="text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase">总访问量 (估)</p>
                       <div className="p-2 bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 rounded-lg"><Users size={16} /></div>
                    </div>
                    <h3 className="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-800">{Math.floor(submissions.length * 2.8) + 12}</h3>
                 </div>

                 <div className="bg-white p-5 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
                    <div className="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
                       <p className="text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase">平均填写耗时</p>
                       <div className="p-2 bg-orange-50 text-orange-600 rounded-lg"><Clock size={16} /></div>
                    </div>
                    <h3 className="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-800">1m 42s</h3>
                 </div>
              </div>

              <div className="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                 {/* Trend Chart */}
                 <div className="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
                    <h3 className="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
                       <TrendingUp size={18} className="text-indigo-500" /> 近7天回收趋势
                    </h3>
                    <div className="h-64">
                       <ResponsiveContainer width="100%" height="100%">
                          <AreaChart data={dailyStats} margin={{top: 10, right: 10, left: 0, bottom: 0}}>
                             <defs>
                                <linearGradient id="colorCount" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
                                   <stop offset="5%" stopColor="#6366f1" stopOpacity={0.3}/>
                                   <stop offset="95%" stopColor="#6366f1" stopOpacity={0}/>
                                </linearGradient>
                             </defs>
                             <CartesianGrid strokeDasharray="3 3" vertical={false} stroke="#f3f4f6" />
                             <XAxis dataKey="name" axisLine={false} tickLine={false} tick={{fontSize: 12, fill: '#9ca3af'}} dy={10} />
                             <YAxis axisLine={false} tickLine={false} tick={{fontSize: 12, fill: '#9ca3af'}} />
                             <Tooltip contentStyle={{borderRadius: '8px', border: 'none', boxShadow: '0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)'}} />
                             <Area type="monotone" dataKey="count" stroke="#6366f1" strokeWidth={3} fillOpacity={1} fill="url(#colorCount)" />
                          </AreaChart>
                       </ResponsiveContainer>
                    </div>
                 </div>

                 {/* Distribution Charts */}
                 {selectFieldStats.length > 0 ? (
                    selectFieldStats.map((stat, idx) => (
                       <div key={idx} className="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
                          <h3 className="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
                             <PieIcon size={18} className="text-purple-500" /> {stat.fieldName} 分布
                          </h3>
                          <div className="h-64 flex items-center justify-center">
                             <ResponsiveContainer width="100%" height="100%">
                                <PieChart>
                                   <Pie
                                      data={stat.data}
                                      cx="50%"
                                      cy="50%"
                                      innerRadius={60}
                                      outerRadius={80}
                                      paddingAngle={5}
                                      dataKey="value"
                                      cornerRadius={6}
                                   >
                                      {stat.data.map((entry, index) => (
                                         <Cell key={`cell-${index}`} fill={COLORS[index % COLORS.length]} strokeWidth={0} />
                                      ))}
                                   </Pie>
                                   <Tooltip contentStyle={{borderRadius: '8px', border: 'none', boxShadow: '0 4px 6px -1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1)'}} />
                                   <Legend verticalAlign="bottom" height={36} iconType="circle" />
                                </PieChart>
                             </ResponsiveContainer>
                          </div>
                       </div>
                    ))
                 ) : (
                    <div className="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-gray-400">
                       <PieIcon size={48} className="mb-4 opacity-20" />
                       <p>暂无选择题数据可分析</p>
                    </div>
                 )}
              </div>
           </div>
        )}
      </div>

      {/* Detail Modal */}
      {selectedSubmission && (
         <div className="fixed inset-0 z-50 flex items-center justify-center p-4 bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-sm" onClick={() => setSelectedSubmission(null)}>
            <div className="bg-white w-full max-w-2xl rounded-2xl shadow-2xl overflow-hidden animate-in fade-in zoom-in duration-200 flex flex-col max-h-[85vh]" onClick={e => e.stopPropagation()}>
               <div className="px-6 py-4 border-b border-gray-100 flex justify-between items-center bg-gray-50">
                  <h3 className="font-bold text-lg text-gray-800">填写详情</h3>
                  <button onClick={() => setSelectedSubmission(null)} className="text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-600"><X size={20} /></button>
               </div>
               <div className="p-6 overflow-y-auto space-y-6">
                  <div className="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mb-2">
                     <div>提交时间: <span className="text-gray-800 font-medium">{new Date(selectedSubmission.submittedAt).toLocaleString()}</span></div>
                     <div>提交ID: <span className="font-mono text-gray-400 text-xs">{selectedSubmission.id}</span></div>
                  </div>
                  <hr className="border-gray-100" />

                  <div className="space-y-6">
                     {form.fields.map(f => {
                        const val = selectedSubmission.data[f.id];
                        return (
                           <div key={f.id}>
                              <label className="text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase mb-1.5 block">{f.label}</label>

                              {f.type === 'SIGNATURE' && val ? (
                                 <div className="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-2 bg-gray-50 inline-block">
                                    <img src={val} alt="Signature" className="h-24 object-contain" />
                                 </div>
                              ) : f.type === 'SCHEDULE' ? (
                                 <div className="bg-gray-50 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 text-sm">
                                    <pre className="font-sans whitespace-pre-wrap">{JSON.stringify(val, null, 2)}</pre>
                                 </div>
                              ) : (
                                 <div className="text-gray-900 font-medium text-base">{String(val || '-')}</div>
                              )}
                           </div>
                        );
                     })}
                  </div>
               </div>
               <div className="p-4 border-t border-gray-100 bg-gray-50 flex justify-end">
                  <button onClick={() => setSelectedSubmission(null)} className="px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-gray-300 rounded-lg text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-50 text-sm font-medium">关闭</button>
               </div>
            </div>
         </div>
      )}
    </div>
  );
};

export default FormAnalytics;

To optimize the Data Report display so it fits within a single interface with an internal scrollbar (avoiding page-level scrolling and clipping issues), I will refactor the layout in `components/FormAnalytics.tsx`.

### **Specification:**

1.  **Fixed Height Layout:**
    *   Set the main container of the analytics view to a fixed height relative to the viewport (e.g., `h-[calc(100vh-140px)]`). This forces the component to fit within the screen area provided by the main app layout.
    *   Use `flex flex-col` to organize the Header, Toolbar, and Table Table.

2.  **Internal Scrolling (The "Slider"):**
    *   The table container will be set to `flex-1 overflow-auto`. This creates a scrollable area specifically for the table data (both vertical and horizontal), while keeping the page headers and toolbars stationary.
    *   This fulfills the request to "add a scrollbar inside the table content box".

3.  **Sticky Headers & Columns:**
    *   **Table Header (`thead`):** Set to `sticky top-0 z-20` with a solid background color (`bg-gray-50`). This ensures column names remain visible while scrolling down.
    *   **Operation Column (Right):** Set to `sticky right-0 z-20` (header) and `z-10` (body) with proper background colors and shadow. This ensures the "View" button is always accessible when scrolling horizontally.
    *   **Z-Index Fix:** Increased z-index for the top-right corner intersection to prevent clipping (overlapping) issues.

4.  **Visual Tweaks:**
    *   Ensure strict background colors on sticky elements to prevent transparency "clipping" (穿模) where text flows underneath transparent headers.

